snippet.title: Diana and Roma's New Dog Adventure
snippet.description:
Diana and Roma have a new pet. This is a cute dog. But they already have a cat, and she is jealous. Diana and Roma are learning how to take care of their new pet Dog. Children try to take care of two animals so that the cat is not jealous and does not feel abandoned.
